name: pet-ufeeder
0:
”Alexa, start pet u. feeder”
”Alexa, open pet u. feeder”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pet u. feeder
des:
for example, your pet-u feeder's name is 'jack', if you want to feeed 1 pack to your pet immediately, say jack feed 1.
or you want to feed 10 packs food to your pet at 21:00, you can say "jack feed 10 at 9 pm".
of you want to play with your pet, you can say "jack shoot" or "jack fire".
